B XCFG
: Xilinx Configuration Utility for DS35 OrCAD interface
 
############################################################################
# Tool description (for program help)
############################################################################
M DESCRIPTION
: This program will modify your SDT.CFG (OrCAD SDT configuration file) [.br]
: and/or VST.CFG (OrCAD VST configuration file) in the current directory [.br]
: so that they are set up to run with the Xilinx OrCAD environment.[.br][.br]
: USAGE: xcfg <family> [[<parameter>=<value> ...][.br][.br]
: EXAMPLE: xcfg 4 x=d:\xact  

############################################################################
# External Parameter Names
# What is this parameter?  This is the...(a short & pithy 1-liner)
############################################################################
M FAMILY
: Xilinx family.

M XACT
: XACT path.

M OL
: Old library option.

M SCO
: SDT configuration only.

M VCO
: VST configuration only.
 
############################################################################
# Help Messages
# What does this parameter do?  This parameter...(verbose multi-liner)
############################################################################
M HFAMILY
: Specifies the number representing the family of Xilinx device to
: be used. The valid numbers are 2 (XC2000), 3 (XC3000), 4 (XC4000),
: 7 (XC7000 EPLD).

M HXACT
: Specifies the Xilinx XACT path. If this option isn't specified,
: it will be set to the value of the XACT environment variable.

M HOL
: This option must be set if you are using the old SDT/VST library
: v4.20 instead of the new unified SDT/VST library from Xilinx.

M HSCO
: If this option is specified, XCFG configures the SDT.CFG file in
: the current directory only.

M HVCO
: If this option is specified, XCFG configures the VST.CFG file in
: the current directory only.

############################################################################
# Warning  Messages
############################################################################
M XILINX_FAMILY_UNSPECIFIED_ERROR
:DS35-XCFG-WARNING-001:[.br]
: The Xilinx family was not specified from the command line.

M INVALID_XILINX_FAMILY_ERROR
> family z
:DS35-XCFG-WARNING-002:[.br]
: An invalid Xilinx device family "[family]" was specified from[.br]
: the command line.[.br]
: The valid families are 2 (XC2000), 3 (XC3000), 4 (XC4000), 7 (EPLD).

M NONEXISTENT_FILE_WARNING
> filename s
:DS35-XCFG-WARNING-003:[.br]
: Could not find the OrCAD configuration file [filename] in[.br]
: current directory.

M NONREADABLE_FILE_WARNING
> filename s
:DS35-XCFG-WARNING-004:[.br]
: The OrCAD configuration file [filename] is not readable.[.br]
: Check the "read" permission on the configuration file.

M FAIL_TO_OPEN_FILE_WARNING
> filename s
:DS35-XCFG-WARNING-005:[.br]
: Fail to open the file [filename].[.br]
: Check the permission of the configuration files or the[.br]
: the directory where these files are located.

M NO_SDT_CONFIG_WARNING
:DS35-XCFG-WARNING-006:[.br]
: No SDT configuration is performed.[.br]

M NO_VST_CONFIG_WARNING
:DS35-XCFG-WARNING-007:[.br]
: No VST configuration is performed.[.br]

M SDTCFG_CREATION_WARNING
:DS35-XCFG-WARNING-008:[.br]
: Failed to create the new SDT configuration file sdt.cfg.[.br]
: The new SDT configuration file is called xcfg.sdt. Check[.br]
: the permission on the sdt.cfg file.

M VSTCFG_CREATION_WARNING
:DS35-XCFG-WARNING-009:[.br]
: Failed to create the new VST configuration file vst.cfg.[.br]
: The new VST configuration file is called xcfg.vst. Check[.br]
: the permission on the vst.cfg file.

############################################################################
# Error  Messages
############################################################################
M OPTIONS_CONFLICTION_ERROR
:DS35-XCFG-ERROR-001:
: The command-line options S and V can not be both TRUE at the same time.

M XACT_ENV_VAR_UNSET_ERROR
:DS35-XCFG-ERROR-002:
: The XACT environment variable is not set.

M DS35_ENV_ERROR
> xactpath s
:DS35-XCFG-ERROR-003:
: The XACT path '[xactpath]' is not set up properly or the[.br]
: Xilinx DS35 OrCAD interface is not installed in the XACT path.

M INVALID_DIRECTORY_PATH_ERROR
> dirpath s
:DS35-XCFG-ERROR-004:
: Invalid directory path [dirpath] is detected.

M SYNTAX_ERROR_IN_FILE
> command s
> filename s
> linenum d
> line z
:DS35-XCFG-ERROR-005:
: A [command] syntax error was detected at linenum [linenum][.br]
: of the file [filename].[.br]
: [line]

############################################################################
# Information Messages
############################################################################
M READ_SDTCFG_FILE
: Reading the SDT configuration file sdt.cfg.
 
M READ_VSTCFG_FILE
: Reading the VST configuration file vst.cfg.
 
E XCFG
